    "description": {
      "chat": "",
      "gmnotes": "",
      "short": "",
      "unidentified": "",
      "value": "<p>As a standard action, a scuriday can expel a 30-foot cone of sound that deals 1d6 sonic damage. At 3rd level, a scuriday adds 1-1/2 × their character level to the damage. A creature in the cone can attempt a Fortitude save for half damage (DC = 10 + half the scuriday’s character level + their Constitution modifier). A scuriday can’t use this ability again until they have taken a 10-minute rest to recover Stamina Points.</p>"
